## Remarks  
<span data-ttu-id="5117a-276">方法释放与关联的<xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>非托管资源和托管资源。 `Close`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5117a-276">The `Close` method frees both unmanaged and managed resources associated with the <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5117a-277">如果拥有基础<xref:System.Net.Sockets.Socket>, 则也会将其关闭。 <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5117a-277">If the <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream> owns the underlying <xref:System.Net.Sockets.Socket>, it is closed as well.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="5117a-278">如果与关联`Close` , 则该方法将关闭 TCP 连接, 但不会释放关联<xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient>的。 <xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient> <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5117a-278">If a <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream> was associated with a <xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient>, the `Close` method will close the TCP connection, but not dispose of the associated <xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient>.</span></span>

